title: Falconshield - Tentakill feat. Nicki Taylor ( Original LoL song - Illaoi )

embed.description: We wanted to create a song that conveyed the ruthless and hard as bone attitude of Illaoi. Her God with her on the battlefield, who'd dare to challenge her? Who would pass the tests? If you want this song as MP3, as well as every other song we release to Youtube for only $1 / month - join the Patreon family!

body:
Una canzone che trasmette l'atteggiamento spietato e duro di Illaoi.
Con la sua Dea con lei sul campo di battaglia, chi oserebbe sfidarla? Chi potrebbe superare le prove?
